%%{init: {"theme":"default"}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor U as Người dùng
    participant HF as HomeFragment
    participant HR as HomeRepository
    participant API as FilmController
    participant SVC as FilmService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>HF: Mở tab Home
    HF->>HR: loadHome()
    HR->>API: GET /films/home
    API->>SVC: getHomeSections()
    SVC->>DB: Truy vấn nhiều bảng (banners, films...)
    DB-->>SVC: Dữ liệu
    SVC-->>API: HomeResponse
    API-->>HR: ApiResponse OK
    HR-->>HF: LiveData update
    HF->>HF: Render 5 RecyclerView sections
    HF-->>U: Hiển thị trang chủ
